To run the new spextool (v4.1) while the old one is installed

first, 
IDL> .com /usr/local/Spextool/pro/ximgtool.pro

second, 

IDL> .com /usr/local/Spextool/pro/xspextool.pro

also need to do 
IDL> .com /prvt/kai/glenn3/astron_lib/pro/fits/mrd_hread.pro
IDL> .com /prvt/kai/glenn3/astron_lib/pro/fits/mrdfits.pro
IDL> .com /prvt/kai/glenn3/astron_lib/pro/fits/fxposit.pro
